trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of documents discovered during XML Web services discovery that have been downloaded to the client.
This class cannot be inherited.

The <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientProtocol.Documents%2A> property of <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientProtocol> is of type <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientDocumentCollection>.
Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientDocumentCollection"></xref> class.
Adds an object with the specified URL to the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientDocumentCollection"></xref>.
The URL for the document to add to the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientDocumentCollection"></xref>.
A discovered document to add to the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientDocumentCollection"></xref>.
url is `null`.
An entry with a key of url already exists in the .
Determines if the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientDocumentCollection"></xref> contains an object with the specified URL.
The URL for the document to locate within the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientDocumentCollection"></xref>.
`true` if the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientDocumentCollection"></xref> contains an object with the specified URL; otherwise, `false`.
url is `null`.
Gets or sets a client discovery document object from the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientDocumentCollection"></xref> with the specified URL.
The URL of the discovery document to get or set from the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientDocumentCollection"></xref>.
An <xref href="System.Object"></xref> representing the document discovered and downloaded to the client.

The underlying type of the object can be a <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription"></xref>, <xref href="System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchema"></xref>, or <xref href="System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryDocument"></xref>.
url is `null`.
Gets an <xref href="System.Collections.ICollection"></xref> object with all the keys in the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientDocumentCollection"></xref>.
An <xref href="System.Collections.ICollection"></xref> containing the keys of the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientDocumentCollection"></xref>.
Removes an object with the specified URL from the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientDocumentCollection"></xref>.
The URL for the discovered document to remove from the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientDocumentCollection"></xref>.
url is `null`.
Gets an <xref href="System.Collections.ICollection"></xref> object with all the values in the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientDocumentCollection"></xref>.
An <xref href="System.Collections.ICollection"></xref> containing the values in the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientDocumentCollection"></xref>.
